at humans are at top of the animal kingdom, it is up to us to rule with conscience. It is up to us to protect and preserve our environment and the wildlife that lives in it.		MARINE MAMMALS (92%); MAMMALS (91%); EDITORIALS and OPINIONS (91%); CLIMATE CHANGE (90%); COASTAL AREAS (90%); WILDLIFE (78%); ZOOS and AQUARIUMS (78%); WATER POLLUTION (77%); ENVIRONMENT and NATURAL RESOURCES (77%); OCEANS (71%); INTERVIEWS (68%)  	MCCLATCHY-TRIBUNE INFORMATION SERVICES (62%)  			CALIFORNIA, USA (79%) UNITED STATES (79%)  	January 23, 2009  	ENGLISH  			Newspaper  	2009    	Palos Verdes Peninsula News, Calif.  			General  		20090122-VT-EDITORIAL-January-22-Editorial-0122  	VT  									
