ighting the path forward, President Obama outlined the right vision for the country. Now let's hope he, and we, are up to the challenge of seeing it through.LiNeBrEaKBOTTOM LINE: President Obama knows what needs to be done. Let's get started.		EDITORIALS and OPINIONS (91%); OBAMA'S FIRST 100 DAYS (91%); TREASURY DEPARTMENTS (76%); EDUCATION SYSTEMS and INSTITUTIONS (72%); AFRICAN AMERICANS (63%); GLOBAL WARMING (54%); US PRESIDENTS (89%)  	MCCLATCHY-TRIBUNE INFORMATION SERVICES (62%)  		BARACK OBAMA (95%)  	UNITED STATES (92%); AFGHANISTAN (79%); IRAQ (79%)  	January 21, 2009  	ENGLISH  			Newspaper  	2009 Anchorage Daily News   	Anchorage Daily News, Alaska  			General  	Distributed by McClatchy-Tribune Business News  	20090121-AC-EDITORIAL-President-Obama-0121  	AC  									
